# Cruds — Simple Product Management System

> Simple CRUDS product management system built with HTML, CSS & JavaScript using localStorage during my learning journey. [Demo](https://your-project.vercel.app)

![Cruds System Screenshot](/imgs/Cruds%20System%20Screenshot.png)

## Quick Overview
- Single-page UI: [main.html](main.html)
- Core JavaScript files: [js/main.js](js/main.js) (Key functions: `inputchek`, `getsearchmood`, `searchFn`)
- CSS styles: [css/main.css](css/main.css), [css/normalize.css](css/normalize.css), [css/template-2.css](css/template-2.css), [css/all.min.css](css/all.min.css)
- Licensed fonts: [Open_Sans/OFL.txt](Open_Sans/OFL.txt), [Open_Sans/README.txt](Open_Sans/README.txt)
- Assets: `imgs/` and `webfonts/` folders

## Features
- Create new products (title, price, taxes, ads, discount, quantity, category)
- Automatic total price calculation
- Search by title or category
- Update and delete products from table
- Simple, customizable, and easy-to-understand design

## How to Run Locally
1. Clone or download the repository
2. Open [main.html](main.html) directly in browser or use Live Server extension
3. Try adding products, searching, updating, or deleting

## Folder Structure
├── main.html # Main display page
├── css/ # Styles (main.css, normalize.css)
├── js/ # App logic (main.js)
├── Open_Sans/ # Fonts & license (OFL.txt)
├── imgs/ # Images
└── webfonts/ # Web fonts

## Technologies Used
- **Frontend**: HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JavaScript
- **Storage**: localStorage
- **Fonts**: Open Sans (OFL licensed)
- **Icons**: Font Awesome

